    The Science of Customized Energy
    Segments
    Segment Headline: Engineered for Fast Absorption
    Headline: Feel It in as little as 5 minutes
    Subhead: CLIME’s gel format bypasses the slow digestive process. Active ingredients absorb through the mouth and upper GI for fast, smooth onset without the sugar rush or crash. 
